title: Abhilasham
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Best Actor
subTitle: A primary school teacher is obsessed with the world of cinema and dreams of becoming an actor one day. However, his blind obsession eventually leads him into a precarious situation.

title: Sarkkar Colony
subTitle: Life in a modest government colony takes a turn as its residents pursue a side venture, hoping to ease financial burdens but ending up in unexpected chaos.

title: Tournament
subTitle: When their flight is delayed, two cricketers, their friend and a photographer embark on a road trip to compete in the selection trials for a tournament. However, they face many challenges en route.

title: Crazy Gopalan
subTitle: Gopalan, a notorious thief, teams up with Lakshmanan and continues to rob people. Their lives change when they kidnap a rich girl and find themselves trapped.

title: Njandukalude Nattil Oridavela
subTitle: Kurian, a naive man, visits home from London expecting for his nuptials. Later, he learns about his mother's cancer and supports her through the treatment.

title: Neyyattinkara Gopante Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: Action Hero Biju
subTitle: Biju Poulose leaves his teaching job to pursue his dream of serving in the police force. Posted as the sub-inspector in Cochin, he has to handle notorious criminals who indulge in unlawful activities.

title: Vettam
subTitle: Gopalakrishnan meets Veena while trying to smuggle a stolen necklace. Later, he accompanies Veena on her mission to unite with her lover.

title: Alibhai
subTitle: Ali Bhai, a goon, is the saviour of the poor in his dominion, Palayam market. However, when his enemies try to take over the market, he goes to great lengths to protect his stronghold and his people.

title: Rain Rain Come Again
subTitle: A fierce college rivalry turns deadly when one group embrace Satanism, unleashing terror by killing their rivals one by one.

title: Aayudham
subTitle: When a powerful explosion occurs at the Vilayam beach seconds after Chief Minister Madhavan leaves the venue, Police Officer Rishikesh is tasked with the investigation to find the truth behind the blast.

subTitle: Raghu, a responsible youth, faces the wrath of the villagers as he is the son of a lazy postman. However, Raghu's life takes a turn when he encounters Yasin Mubarak, a notorious man.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Drishyam
subTitle: When his daughter accidentally kills a man in self-defence, Georgekutty uses his film knowledge to cover it up. Even when the investigation catches up with them, Georgekutty looks out for his family.

title: Swapnakoodu
subTitle: Three men compete against each other to win the affections of a beautiful woman. However, complications arise when her mother suffers from a heart attack.

title: Manjummel Boys
subTitle: After one of them falls inside a dangerous pit in the Guna Caves, a group of childhood friends muster courage to rescue him out of a space from where a return is next to impossible.

title: Rasathanthram
subTitle: Premachandran, a carpenter, rescues Kanmani, an ill-treated maid, and takes her into his care. However, to escape from her former abusers, Kanmani dresses up as a boy and joins the team of carpenters.

title: Srungaravelan
subTitle: Kanan falls in love with Raddhu, the daughter of a ruthless city gangster responsible for numerous deaths. To marry her, Kanan must confront the dangers and challenges that lie ahead.

title: Vairam
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Film Star
subTitle: A struggling writer dreams of turning his life story into a film starring a famous actor, but unexpected twists challenge both men's perspectives as they navigate the unpredictable world of cinema.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: Oru Vadakkan Selfie
subTitle: When his father asks him to manage their grocery store, Umesh runs away to Chennai to become a film-maker. His life changes after he takes a selfie with his old neighbour and posts it online.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: Sreekrishnapurathe Nakshathrathilakkam
subTitle: Three out of four brothers of a Malayali household are happily married while the fourth brother is engaged. When the beautiful Yamuna Rani becomes their new neighbour, she poses a threat to the wives.

title: Jaya Jaya Jaya Jaya Hey
subTitle: Jayabharathi, an ambitious girl, strives to complete her education. However, when her parents marry her off, she attempts to carve an identity for herself.

title: Mumbai Police
subTitle: ACP Antony Moses has managed to track down his friend's killer when he meets with an accident resulting in partial memory loss. Soon, he is reassigned to investigate the murder and find the culprit.
